episodes.title: Episode #1.1
episodes.plot: Angry, pervy, outrageous and hilarious Fleabag arrives with a bang, as she spins through the city grasping at anyone and anything that might keep her head above water.

episodes.title: Episode #1.2
episodes.plot: Fleabag attempts to rekindle romantic fires to distract her from the mayhem of her life.

episodes.title: Episode #1.3
episodes.plot: Fleabag helps her inappropriate brother-in-law buy a present for Claire, who is organising her own surprise birthday party. Fleabag reconnects with a toothy friend.

episodes.title: Episode #1.4
episodes.plot: Fleabag and her sister visit a female-only silent retreat, courtesy of their father. Their enforced silence is interrupted by an unusual neighbouring weekend workshop

episodes.title: Episode #1.5
episodes.plot: On the anniversary of her mother's death, Fleabag and Claire return to their family home for the annual memorial lunch.

episodes.title: Episode #1.6
episodes.plot: Fleabag faces up to her actions and reveals what happened to her beloved friend Boo.
